{"question":"Is mobile phone allowed in class?","answer":"Usage of mobile phones during lectures is generally prohibited. They should be kept on silent mode or switched off.","category":"Campus Life","keywords":["mobile","phone","class rules"],"_id":"3KXZnuUC1UM9OPJr"}
{"question":"Is Ragging allowed?","answer":"No, GITAM has a strict zero-tolerance policy towards ragging. Anti-ragging committees ensure a safe environment for all students.","category":"Student Support","keywords":["ragging","safety","anti-ragging"],"_id":"3Oj4Z9OR0c7Un6XS"}
{"question":"Are there sports facilities available?","answer":"Yes, GITAM has extensive sports facilities including cricket grounds, tennis courts, basketball courts, indoor stadiums, and gyms.","category":"Facilities","keywords":["sports","gym","cricket","games"],"_id":"3SbGAy8NkN1BwSV8"}
