{"question":"When is Commencement of Classwork (Even Semester)?","answer":"Commencement of Classwork (Even Semester) is scheduled on 2025-12-15. Start of classes for Even Semester.","category":"Academic Calendar","keywords":["Commencement","calendar","date","2025","2026"],"_id":"3rV4iuIAGeKUQHrW"}
