{"question":"Can I do a part-time job?","answer":"Full-time programs require full commitment. However, some internships or 'earn-while-you-learn' schemes may be available.","category":"Student Support","keywords":["part-time","job","work"],"_id":"9WOFR9OpPgvSjlTB"}
