{"question":"What is the placement eligibility?","answer":"Eligibility depends on company criteria, but generally, students with a CGPA above 6.0 or 6.5 and no active backlogs are eligible for most companies.","category":"Placements","keywords":["eligibility","placement","criteria"],"_id":"JVKiOy0BhrdeB6R8"}
