{"question":"What are the eligibility criteria for B.Tech?","answer":"For B.Tech, candidates typically need a minimum of 60% aggregate marks in Intermediate (10+2) or equivalent with Physics, Chemistry, and Mathematics. Rank in GAT or JEE Main is also required.","category":"Admissions","keywords":["eligibility","B.Tech","requirements","marks"],"_id":"M4RGWwMmvOq9kulx"}
