{"question":"Are there hostel facilities for boys and girls?","answer":"Yes, GITAM provides separate hostel facilities for boys and girls at all three campuses (Visakhapatnam, Hyderabad, Bengaluru) with modern amenities.","category":"Facilities","keywords":["hostel","accommodation","boys","girls"],"_id":"NC2NsPcZNMHgYfot"}
