{"question":"What is the average package?","answer":"The average package for Engineering graduates typically ranges between INR 4.5 to 6 LPA, depending on the branch and market conditions.","category":"Placements","keywords":["average package","salary","median"],"_id":"R97neK9TO2CZYo7p"}
