{"question":"Are parents allowed to visit hostels?","answer":"Parents can visit their wards in the hostel visitor lounge during designated visiting hours.","category":"Facilities","keywords":["parents","visitors","hostel"],"_id":"TptWcdWrSN06ckwx"}
{"question":"What is the biggest fest at GITAM?","answer":"The annual cultural and techno-management fest (often called GUSAC Carnival or Pramana/GEMS depending on campus) is the biggest event, attracting students from across the country.","category":"Campus Life","keywords":["fest","cultural","event","carnival"],"_id":"UPOGQj61nRVm4Qr9"}
{"question":"Is there a makeup exam?","answer":"Supplementary exams serve as makeup exams for those who failed.","category":"Academics","keywords":["makeup","exam","retry"],"_id":"UhXVK6F5hWu6Ngrk"}
{"question":"Is there an EV charging station?","answer":"Some campuses may have charging points for electric vehicles.","category":"Facilities","keywords":["charging","station","EV"],"_id":"Uiktk8eOyE5Kfrkh"}
{"question":"Is exam schedule flexible?","answer":"No, exam schedules are fixed by the Controller of Examinations. Rescheduling is done only in extreme emergencies.","category":"Academics","keywords":["exam","schedule","timetable"],"_id":"Uw2JqdjhjSiF5Zyk"}
{"question":"What acts constitute indiscipline?","answer":"Ragging, damaging property, smoking/drinking on campus, and disrupting classes are considered acts of indiscipline.","category":"Student Support","keywords":["indiscipline","rules","bad behavior"],"_id":"V9taWESlSBRHeoOO"}
{"question":"Who to contact for ragging complaints?","answer":"You can contact the Anti-Ragging helpline or the principal/director of your institute immediately.","category":"Student Support","keywords":["complaint","ragging","helpline"],"_id":"VdoxSAyL6CC8Y8ER"}
{"question":"Are there research opportunities for undergraduates?","answer":"Yes, undergraduate students are encouraged to participate in research projects under faculty guidance and can join research forums like GUSAC.","category":"Academics","keywords":["research","undergraduate","projects"],"_id":"VyGeg6A1PLeNVIjL"}
{"question":" Is there a guest house?","answer":"Yes, the university has guest houses to accommodate visiting faculty, parents, and guests.","category":"Facilities","keywords":["guest house","stay","accommodation"],"_id":"W8FXiNhxCJi4MW7z"}
{"question":"Is there a convocation ceremony?","answer":"Yes, Convocation is held annually where degrees are awarded to graduating students.","category":"Academics","keywords":["convocation","graduation","degree"],"_id":"WPtrKBNJR421HkSr"}
{"question":"Is outside food allowed?","answer":"Generally, outside food delivery is allowed to the gate/hostel entrance, but rules vary.","category":"Facilities","keywords":["food","outside","delivery"],"_id":"WjANrjm3l896nnix"}
{"question":"How to clear backlogs?","answer":"Register for the backlog subjects when the supplementary exam notification is released.","category":"Academics","keywords":["backlog","clear","exam"],"_id":"X2XhHbpYg25Dysec"}
{"question":"Can I bring my laptop to campus?","answer":"Yes, students are encouraged to bring laptops for academic purposes. Wi-Fi is available.","category":"Campus Life","keywords":["laptop","gadgets"],"_id":"XOudFqSTRsNMpjuN"}
{"question":"How is the water quality?","answer":"Water is treated and strictly monitored for quality and safety.","category":"Facilities","keywords":["water","quality","health"],"_id":"Xdv0gBasYBbh81Vd"}
{"question":"Are there language labs?","answer":"Yes, English Language Communication Skills (ELCS) labs help students improve their speaking and listening skills.","category":"Academics","keywords":["language lab","english","skills"],"_id":"Y0dHwBCQVvRP0r9H"}
{"question":"How do I apply for a hostel?","answer":"Hostel rooms are allotted on a first-come, first-served basis. You can apply for hostel accommodation during the admission counseling process.","category":"Facilities","keywords":["hostel booking","apply","room"],"_id":"Y77tjzOaacyT7xpf"}
{"question":"What documents are required during counseling?","answer":"Commonly required documents include 10th and 12th mark sheets, GAT/Entrance rank card, Transfer Certificate (TC), Conduct Certificate, Transfer Certificate, and ID proof (Aadhar).","category":"Admissions","keywords":["documents","certificates","counseling"],"_id":"YHjbZSHBAJo4I1mN"}
{"question":"When is Summer Vacation?","answer":"Summer Vacation is scheduled on 2026-05-01 to 2026-06-30. Summer break for students.","category":"Academic Calendar","keywords":["Summer","calendar","date","2025","2026"],"_id":"Z5Bj6Et63vpmRDTg"}
{"question":"Can I change my branch after admission?","answer":"Branch change is subject to university policy, usually allowed after the first year based on academic performance (CGPA) and vacancy in the desired branch.","category":"Admissions","keywords":["branch change","transfer","first year"],"_id":"ZHG8qWmfai1n8J29"}
{"question":"When is Sessional-I Examinations?","answer":"Sessional-I Examinations is scheduled on 2025-10-06 to 2025-10-14. First mid-term examinations for Odd Semester.","category":"Academic Calendar","keywords":["Sessional-I","calendar","date","2025","2026"],"_id":"ZMRZrpiQKMh3Rv3t"}
{"question":"Where is GITAM Visakhapatnam located?","answer":"GITAM Visakhapatnam is located at Gandhi Nagar, Rushikonda, Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh 530045.","category":"General Info","keywords":["location","address","vizag"],"_id":"ZcYgnUsDTpjMpOOz"}
{"question":"What is 'detained'?","answer":"Detained means not allowed to write exams due to shortage of attendance or credits.","category":"Academics","keywords":["detained","attendance","block"],"_id":"ZrlPweNneXMLsZpG"}
