{"question":"Are placements common for all campuses?","answer":"Yes, GITAM often organizes centralized placement drives where students from Visakhapatnam, Hyderabad, and Bengaluru campuses participate together.","category":"Placements","keywords":["centralized","campuses","common placement"],"_id":"aZmDZj8mWMUEQYyd"}
