{"question":"Does GITAM offer foreign exchange programs?","answer":"Yes, GITAM has collaborations with several international universities for student exchange programs, study abroad semesters, and joint research.","category":"Academics","keywords":["study abroad","exchange","international"],"_id":"bAHsCLQ8OIRbpMJe"}
{"question":"Is plastic allowed?","answer":"GITAM aims to be a plastic-free campus and discourages the use of single-use plastics.","category":"Campus Life","keywords":["plastic","environment","green"],"_id":"bJOtcBPG3qWpVp1S"}
