{"question":"Can I stay in the hostel during vacations?","answer":"Hostels generally close during long summer vacations, but permission may be granted for internships or special classes.","category":"Facilities","keywords":["vacation","hostel","stay"],"_id":"kGjnJM4pGwsYvKTA"}
