{"question":"What is the application fee for GAT?","answer":"The application fee for GAT is typically around INR 1,200, but it is subject to change. Please check the official admission notification for the current year's fee.","category":"Admissions","keywords":["application fee","cost","GAT price"],"_id":"m9Brj3tUNdb0zTNQ"}
