{"question":"What is the motto of GITAM?","answer":"'Strive, Serve, Thrive' or similar values promoting excellence and service. (Check current motto on website)","category":"General Info","keywords":["motto","values"],"_id":"mfrJJwquE9kB1zQz"}
{"question":"How to apply for a duplicate ID card?","answer":"Report the loss to the administration, pay the penalty fee, and apply for a replacement ID card.","category":"Student Support","keywords":["ID card","lost","duplicate"],"_id":"mupjBe3f4T20KAkV"}
