{"question":"Is GITAM a deemed university?","answer":"Yes, GITAM (Gandhi Institute of Technology and Management) is a Deemed to be University accredited by NAAC with 'A++' grade.","category":"General Info","keywords":["deemed","university","accreditation","NAAC"],"_id":"n7DxQdbTXqcoQN98"}
{"question":"Can I park my vehicle on campus?","answer":"Designated parking areas are available for student 2-wheelers and 4-wheelers. Passes may be required.","category":"Facilities","keywords":["parking","vehicle","bike"],"_id":"nS4c9KY72497T3v3"}
