{"question":"What is the counseling process?","answer":"After the results, qualified candidates are called for counseling. You need to choose your preferred campus and branch based on your rank and availability of seats.","category":"Admissions","keywords":["counseling","seat allotment","process"],"_id":"t4Ds3uXT53crQQeS"}
