{"question":" What is the 'Mentor-Mentee' system?","answer":"Each student is assigned a faculty mentor who guides them academically and personally throughout their course.","category":"Academics","keywords":["mentor","guide","support"],"_id":"tORX6uNfKEA4comr"}
{"question":"What is the grading system at GITAM?","answer":"GITAM follows the Choice Based Credit System (CBCS). Performance is evaluated using a 10-point CGPA scale based on internal assessments and semester-end examinations.","category":"Academics","keywords":["grading","CGPA","system","CBCS"],"_id":"u2P1z5gigxhOAsMA"}
